  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1. open status and create new account (no biometrics enabled)\r\n2. settings -> profile -> change password\r\n3. set new password and confirm\r\n\r\nAs result, the prompt for biometrics is shown , even i was not setting any biometrics yet.\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\n\r\n1. rename `Change password` button to `Change password and restart Status`\r\n2.1. _if user doesn't have biometrics enabled_, when clicking the button, user should see the prompt that forces him to logout\r\n2.2. _if user has biometrics enabled_, we don't update the old password with the new one, but let user see the prompt that forces him to logout and offer him on the next app run to update the keychain password with the new one\r\n\r\n**Design:** https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=2204%3A243829\r\n",
