    "body": "> Current sequence: change password dialog appeared, and after saving the new password appeared biometrics and sign out & quit. Should I change this sequence?\r\n\r\nThe design doesn't seem up to date and I don't have a Mac to test it out.\r\n\r\nMaybe it's worth to go on Status and ping the designers about this. I'm not exactly sure what is the wanted behaviour when a user has biometrics and we want to change passwords. It seems from looking at the designs here https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=1023%3A298171&t=B3OUN2Z3OxBLYdiN-0 that if you set biometrics, you don't actually use a password.\r\n\r\nSo I'm guessing the goal here is to make it so that if you were using biometrics, but want to change it to using password, we go back to the password creation screen?\r\nAnyway, ask a designer to clarify. Mario is in charge of onboarding, but Ben and Julia and in charge of profile, so might as well ping all 3 lol",
