    "body": "Question: user has biometrics enabled. He is trying to change the password (settings -> profile -> change password). What's the expectation?\r\n1. Set the new password -> to confirm with biometric -> restart the app\r\n2. Confirm with biometrics the decision to change the password -> restart the app -> on the next app run to update the keychain password with the new one\r\n\r\nBehavior when biometrics is turned off: Set the new password -> to restart the app\r\n\r\nFor me, the correct answer is 1 as it has the same sequence as without biometrics, but I have an old bug (from September) with the description, that the correct sequence with enabled biometrics is 2.\r\n\r\nWho can help me to find the correct behavior?",
